    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of a species containing over 20 subspecies and up to 80 varieties of shaggy-haired bear native to Europe, Asia, and northwestern North America.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
